    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7929546>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28 & 29. Taxa recognized within Gauhatiana Gupta, 1953. 28. Gauhatiana batrachii Gupta, 1953, ventral view, redrawn from Gupta (1953, fig. 7). 29. Gauhatiana lebedevi Gupta & Miglani, 1976, ventral view, redrawn from Gupta & Miglani (1976, fig. 1). Abbreviations:AT, anterior testis; BS, body spines; Ce, cecum; CP, cirrus-pouch; Es, esophagus; GA, genital atrium; GP, genital pore; Me, metraterm; OS, oral sucker; Ov, ovary; PC, prostatic cells; Ph, pharynx; PP, pars prostatica; PT, posterior testis; SR, seminal receptacle; SV, seminal vesicle; Ut, uterus; VD, vitelline duct; V-D, vas-deferens; VF, vitelline follicle; VS, ventral sucker. Scale bars: Fig. 28 = 300 µm; Fig. 29 = 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7929546/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

